title: Out Of Brooklyn
description:
Tony Kornheiser and Michael Wilbon discuss their thoughts on Steve Nash being out as Nets' head coach, if last night’s rainout benefits the Phillies more than the Astros and who the biggest winner was at the NFL trade deadline.
